precis:
Amendment to the Schedule to Order in Council P.C. 1999-1889 which corrects
an error in the reference to a Township Plan in the legal description of
the land thereby set apart for the BEARDY'S & OKEMASIS BAND as an addition
to their Reserve No. 96 & 97-A, in Saskatchewan.
